<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>鈺雯粉絲團</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #8A2BE2;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #8A2BE2;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .comments textarea {
      width: 100%;
      height: 80px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .comments button {
      background-color: #8A2BE2;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .comments-list {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .comment {
      background-color: #eee;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .gallery, .videos, .media-reports {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .gallery img, .videos iframe {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 240px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .videos iframe {
      height: 135px;
    }
    .media-reports a {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>鈺雯粉絲團</h1>
    <p>一起支持最有行動力的檢察官！</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <h2>粉絲數：<span id="fan-count">2,587</span> 人</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>三大貢獻</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>主動出擊：</strong>值勤時主動發掘線索，指揮警力查緝毒販。</li>
        <li><strong>刨根究底：</strong>溯源查獲製毒工廠與毒品原料，查扣大量毒品與犯罪所得。</li>
        <li><strong>守護民安：</strong>有效防止新興毒品流入市面，維護市民健康。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>照片牆</h2>
      <div class="gallery">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/240x160?text=照片1" alt="照片1">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/240x160?text=照片2" alt="照片2">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/240x160?text=照片3" alt="照片3">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>影片專區</h2>
      <div class="videos">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" title="影片1" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oHg5SJYRHA0" title="影片2" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>媒體報導</h2>
      <div class="media-reports">
        <a href="#" target="_blank">自由時報：檢察官黃鈺雯破獲大規模製毒工廠</a>
        <a href="#" target="_blank">聯合報：鈺雯檢察官主導重大毒品案件</a>
        <a href="#" target="_blank">中時新聞：從持毒者追查到集團首腦</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section comments">
      <h2>留言支持鈺雯</h2>
      <textarea id="comment-input" placeholder="留下你的鼓勵或想說的話..."></textarea>
      <br>
      <button onclick="addComment()">送出留言</button>
      <div class="comments-list" id="comments"></div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    function addComment() {
      const input = document.getElementById('comment-input');
      const commentText = input.value.trim();
      if (commentText) {
        const commentDiv = document.createElement('div');
        commentDiv.className = 'comment';
        commentDiv.textContent = commentText;
        document.getElementById('comments').prepend(commentDiv);
        input.value = '';
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
